rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819bbd0253666fdb92ce741c038f1e2ac7abf4a3","tid":444764,"uid":80570,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T18:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以前成日信d仆街做壞事會有報應<br />\n有d仲飛黃騰達<br />\n做好人擔屎唔偷食跟本係on9仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返學如是  d仆街 free ride成組人走去exchange 執靚CV   未grad已有大公司offer<br />\n返工如是  d係後面講你壞話數鳩你既仆街  升職快過同期 ＋ 上兩期人 <br />\n拍拖如是  知d 仆街背後玩女玩到死  溝條乖乖女扮好仔又婚都結埋<br />\n<br />\n唉  好灰<br />\n跟本做仆街先係正確人生玩法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853256460c2c017cbd1de591d039ee3365c9f157","tid":444764,"uid":38539,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"用得失去衡量善惡，究竟係善定惡？<br />\n樓主又如何介定 善和惡？"},{"pid":"f161362b76a046fd87298b18c5748e692158d2f9","tid":444764,"uid":113546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:24:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用得失去衡量善惡，究竟係善定惡？<br />\n樓主又如何介定 善和惡？</blockquote><br />\n好問題"},{"pid":"2d3d004a310872dc4f818d3c62312c7fd2e01b8c","tid":444764,"uid":80570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T21:12:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用得失去衡量善惡，究竟係善定惡？<br />\n樓主又如何介定 善和惡？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好有哲學味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但一件事有得客觀咁睇既我覺得<br />\n好似你係背後數鳩同事   好難係善喎<br />\n幫人利已既咪善行   損人利已既咪惡行"},{"pid":"7864387bb172b4df776b42f37c9732fa62f4e828","tid":444764,"uid":30070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T21:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1e34cc679e143dc87ff49e7a1e27d41f79313c","tid":444764,"uid":58316,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T21:50:26.000Z","msg":"世上有好人<br />\n世上有賤人<br />\n成功既唔一定係賤人<br />\n失敗既唔一定係好人<br />\n總之你做出成績<br />\n冇人在乎你好人定賤人<br />\n好人可以如意亦可以唔如意<br />\n賤人可以如意亦可以唔如意<br />\n成敗同你係好人賤人冇關係<br />\n成功唔係因為你好而加許你<br />\n失敗唔係因為你賤而懲罰你<br />\n成功就成功<br />\n失敗就失敗<br />\n係就係<br />\n唔係就唔係"},{"pid":"98e0c2a6d102d78acd7fa3c2118cfed4959c20c3","tid":444764,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T21:54:41.000Z","msg":"有錢人可以做慈善家，亦可以行老正<br />\n窮人可以安貧樂道，亦可以偷呃拐騙"},{"pid":"f4bdbe19c0bf4f7bf739ecf3d24e3658d657f54c","tid":444764,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T21:56:32.000Z","msg":"做人有時唔洗太過老實<br />\n冇商不奸"},{"pid":"d178599cb4a1565f217fc708c4a7d40a99406cdb","tid":444764,"uid":80570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:46:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>世上有好人<br />\n世上有賤人<br />\n成功既唔一定係賤人<br />\n失敗既唔一定係好人<br />\n總之你做出成績<br />\n冇人在乎你好人定賤人<br />\n好人可以如意亦可以唔如意<br />\n賤人可以如意亦可以唔如意<br />\n成敗同你係好人賤人冇關係<br />\n成功唔係因為你好而加許你<br />\n失敗唔係因為你賤而懲罰你<br />\n成功就成功<br />\n失敗就失敗<br />\n係就係<br />\n唔係就唔係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係由細到大講個d 報應論都係呃9 人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位巴打講得岩 可能我根本係on9 左"},{"pid":"8a90dbacc2ab43a6536ce8905f7381cc379046a5","tid":444764,"uid":69275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:52:49.000Z","msg":"話唔定報應未到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通班仆街十年後末期cancer又比你預知到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897780151b9f578af4542c9979d6b5910981bd97","tid":444764,"uid":56432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:55:22.000Z","msg":"通常冇財冇勢嘅人先至會有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea6ddbf01155d92bb60f6ee3501a26178358ffd","tid":444764,"uid":80570,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T19:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話唔定報應未到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通班仆街十年後末期cancer又比你預知到咩<img src=\"/assets/fac